lead_paragraph: Bournemouth beat south coast rivals Southampton 2-0 in an uninspiring match at Dean Court with the victory keeping the home side eight points clear of the Premier League relegation zone.

headline.print_headline: Bournemouth See Off Neighbours Southampton in Dour Match
